This is the ELEC 3040/3050 textbook. This is intended to use the IBM Publishing Systems BookMaster package on EVIEVM, and can be formatted as follows:
SCRIPT CEMB (OPT(BOOK4PS)

BOOK4PS OPTIONS is present in this repository. Note that this uses the BookMaster Gothic font in the document; this is available at:
http://evievm.pubvm.org/eweb/bookfnt.tar

Evie Cooper, wec0007@auburn.edu
